OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F404A1776967869
OL,3,CTeenager held at Feltham Young
OL,4,COffenders' Institution dies
OL,6,FA 16 year old boy who was being held
OL,7,Fat Feltham Young Offender's
OL,8,Finstitution has died, the Metropolitan
OL,9,FPolice has said.
OL,11,FThe London Ambulance Service was
OL,12,Fcalled to the prison at around 21.30,
OL,13,Fafter receiving reports of an "unwell
OL,14,Fchild".
OL,16,FThe boy was taken to hospital, where
OL,17,Fhe died just over two hours later.
OL,19,FA spokesperson for the Metropolitan
OL,20,FPolice said:
