PN,40402
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F404A1776967869
OL,3,CTeenager held at Feltham Young
OL,4,COffenders' Institution dies
OL,6,F"On Tuesday, 21 April at 00:05hrs,
OL,7,Fpolice were notified by staff at
OL,8,FFeltham Prison and Young Offender
OL,9,FInstitute about the death of a boy who
OL,10,Fhad been found unresponsive and later
OL,11,Fdied in hospital.
OL,13,F"The London Ambulance Service were
OL,14,Fcalled at around 21:30hrs on Monday,
OL,15,F20 April and treated the boy, aged 16,
OL,16,Fbefore taking him to hospital. He
OL,17,Fsadly died at 23:43hrs.
OL,26,@nD@AOUuD@AOU
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G2/4
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,405,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F404A1776967869
OL,3,CTeenager held at Feltham Young
OL,4,COffenders' Institution dies
OL,6,F"At this stage, the death is being
OL,7,Ftreated as unexpected. A post-mortem
OL,8,Fexamination is scheduled for Friday,
OL,9,F24 April. Officers are working at pace
OL,10,Fto establish the full circumstances
OL,11,Fand are pursuing all lines of inquiry."
OL,13,FA Youth Custody Service spokesperson
OL,14,Fsaid:
OL,16,F"We were saddened to hear of the death
OL,17,Fof a child from YOI Feltham, who died
OL,18,Fin hospital on Monday 20 April, and
OL,19,Four thoughts are with their friends
OL,20,Fand family.
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@gO]xD@AOU
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G3/4
