PN,40404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F404A1776967869
OL,3,CTeenager held at Feltham Young
OL,4,COffenders' Institution dies
OL,6,F"As with all deaths in custody, the
OL,7,FPrisons and Probation Ombudsman will
OL,8,Finvestigate. It would be inappropriate
OL,9,Fto comment further at this time."
